dentified war as the sixth (of ten) biggest problems facing humanity for the next fifty years.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>","created_on":"2012-11-28T17:18:48","latitude":null,"geohash":"","short_permalink":"/web/20150108141741/http://www.breakingnews.com\/t\/P","image_credit":"Photo: <a href=\"/web/20150108141741/http://en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/War\">Wikipedia<\/a>","item_count":27735,"category":"Topic","local_url":"\/topic\/war-conflict\/","kind":"vertical","muted_by_default":false,"links":"","daily_count":60,"livevideo":"","items_resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/?topics=15","moderation_status":"approved","twitter_username":null,"slug":"war-conflict","related_topics_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/?related_to=15","facebookchat":"","recent_count":12,"latest_item_date":"2015-01-08T14:11:42.155484","wikipedia_url":"/web/20150108141741/http://en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/War","name":"war & conflict","permalink":"/web/20150108141741/http://www.breakingnews.com\/topic\/war-conflict\/","image_url":"/web/20150108141741/http://upload.wikimedia.org\/wikipedia\/commons\/a\/a7\/Cyprian_War.jpg","placetype":"","resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/15\/","active":true,"woeid":null}],"content":"Paris police name 2 police officers killed at Charlie Hebdo building as Franck Brinsolaro and Ahmed Merabet - @NBCNews","url":"","type":"text","slug":"paris-police-name-2-police-officers-killed-at-char","url_domain":null,"status":"published","pushed":true,"push_content":"Paris police name 2 police officers killed at Charlie Hebdo building as Franck Brinsolaro and Ahmed Merabet - @NBCNews","id":494420,"permalink":"/web/20150108141741/http://www.breakingnews.com\/item\/2015\/01\/08\/paris-police-name-2-police-officers-killed-at-char","data_type":null,"media":null,"tweet":null,"updated_date":"2015-01-08T13:58:23.275652","resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/494420\/","data":null,"date":"2015-01-08T13:45:54.891329"},{"note":null,"author":{"full_name":"David Wyllie","email":"david.wyllie@breakingnews.com","id":12,"last_name":"Wyll