mmunity sentence, imprisonment, life imprisonment or, in some jurisdictions, even death.<\/p>\r\n<p>To be classified as a crime, the act of doing something bad (actus reus) must be usually accompanied by the intention to do something bad (mens rea), with certain exceptions (strict liability).<\/p>\r\n<p>While every crime violates the law, not every violation of the law counts as a crime. Breaches of private law (torts and breaches of contract) are not automatically punished by the state, but can be enforced through civil procedure.<\/p>\r\n<p><\/p>","created_on":"2012-11-28T17:18:53","latitude":null,"geohash":"","short_permalink":"/web/20150108141741/http://www.breakingnews.com\/t\/B","image_credit":"Photo: <a href=\"/web/20150108141741/http://en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Crime\">Wikipedia<\/a>","item_count":49782,"category":"Topic","local_url":"\/topic\/crime-courts\/","kind":"vertical","muted_by_default":false,"links":"","daily_count":130,"livevideo":"","items_resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/item\/?topics=1","moderation_status":"approved","twitter_username":null,"slug":"crime-courts","related_topics_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/?related_to=1","facebookchat":"","recent_count":18,"latest_item_date":"2015-01-08T14:11:42.155484","wikipedia_url":"/web/20150108141741/http://en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Crime","name":"crime & courts","permalink":"/web/20150108141741/http://www.breakingnews.com\/topic\/crime-courts\/","image_url":"/web/20150108141741/http://upload.wikimedia.org\/wikipedia\/commons\/4\/4b\/Pierre-Paul_Prud%27hon_-_Justice_and_Divine_Vengeance_Pursuing_Crime.JPG","placetype":"","resource_uri":"\/api\/v1\/topic\/1\/","active":true,"woeid":null}],"content":"Photo: Gas station robbed in Villers-Cotteret, Picardy, around 50 miles northeast of Paris, which may be connected to search for fugitives - @SophGarratt","url":"/web/20150108141741/https://twitter.com\/SophGarratt\/status\/553164202622599168\/photo\/1","type":"text","slug":"photo-gas-station-robbed-in-villers-cotteret-pic","u